      "text": "- Identify clients by user id , ips, api key \n- Limit requests based on configurable rules ( so no code dependencies)\n- Return Proper error code and meaningful ratelimit headers\n- Aaalytics on rate limiting data \n- Long term persistance of data ",
      "fontSize": 19.337081847116238,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Identify clients by user id , ips, api key \n- Limit requests based on configurable rules ( so no code dependencies)\n- Return Proper error code and meaningful ratelimit headers\n- Aaalytics on rate limiting data \n- Long term persistance of data ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
